OL,6,     FScotland v Morocco (Kick-off
OL,7,     F11.00pm). Mark Pougatch presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group C match at
OL,9,     FBoston Stadium in the USA. This is
OL,10,     Fthe second World Cup meeting
OL,11,     Fbetween these nations, with the
OL,12,     Fprevious one also being a
OL,13,     Fgroup-stage match at France '98,
OL,14,     Fthe last time Scotland appeared at
OL,15,     Fthe finals. It was the Africans
OL,16,     Fwho came out on top with a
OL,17,     Fcomfortable 3-0 win in
OL,18,     FSaint-Etienne over a side that
OL,19,     Ffeatured the likes of Jim
OL,20,     FLeighton, Colin Hendry, John
OL,21,     FCollins and Gordon Durie, and was
OL,22,     Fmanaged by Craig Brown. Morocco
